Rohan Cornelius Ash (born 18 August 1976) is a Saint Vincent-born cricketer who plays for the Turks and Caicos Islands.  Ash is a right-handed batsman who bowls right-arm off break.
Ash played a single Twenty20 match for the Turks and Caicos Islands against Montserrat in the 2008 Stanford 20/20 at the Stanford Cricket Ground.  He was dismissed for 9 runs in this match by Lionel Baker, with the Turks and Caicos Islands making just 67 runs in their twenty overs.  Montserrat went on to win the match by 9 wickets.
